1. 💵 **CASH** — bartender marks cash received (no change from today).
2. 🖥️ **CARD / UPI** — single button → tablet POSTs amount to Pine Labs Plutus on local LAN → machine prompts customer "Tap card / Scan QR / Wallet" → customer chooses on machine → machine returns paymentId → tablet calls `verifyRechargePayment` → wallet credits with `serverVerified:true`. Pine Labs settles ALL methods (Visa/Master/Rupay/UPI/Sodexo) into single bank deposit.
